<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Golozar%20A"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Asieh Golozar</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Fagundes%20RB"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id2"><span class="name western">Renato B Fagundes</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id2">
