<sup>4</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Kamangar%20F"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id5"><span class="name western">Farin Kamangar</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id5">
<h3><span class="name western">Farin Kamangar</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Division of Cancer Epidemiology and Genetics, National Cancer Institute, Bethesda, MD, USA</div>
<div class="p">
