<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Kamangar%20F"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Farin Kamangar</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1,</sup><sup>5</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Abnet%20CC"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id6"><span class="name western">Christian C Abnet</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id6">
<h3><span class="name western">Christian C Abnet</span></h3>
<div class="p">
